<br>
Worst thing you can do is try it for a bit and find out I don't know what I am saying and go with the other combo mentioned here.  I think you may be suprised though.  I have a crafted velium warsword (10/18, no stats, no procs) and the aggro generated by it seems to be crap for me compared to my Lurid dagger (12/20 procs shadow creep AC tap).  Even when the dagger doesn't proc much it feels like I do more damage and aggro control is better.  To be honest, I haven't parsed damage or anything like that, I go by feel.  This is a game and supposed to be fun and that just seems like too much work to put into a game.  I collect and analyze enough data in RL being and engineer that I do not want to do more of it in a game.<br>
<br>
Just another option,<br>
<br>
Friedrick - 58th Myrmidom on Tunare server<br>
